/* ============================================================
   Mavericks Fit Call Practice
   - The real deck fills the stage. The teleprompter under it shows
     the exact words to say, screen one is the full intro: welcome,
     explain, set the definite outcome, get the yes.
   - Mav AI is a collapsible side drawer that follows the deck.
   - Mav runs live on the Anthropic API in this preview. A hosted
     build needs a backend proxy so the key stays server side.
============================================================ */

